**  @MS  ( ERR MSG )
ER01 SELECT "0" OR "1"
ER02 ERROR!!
ER03 NOT FOUND
ER04 PRODUCT QTY SHOULD NOT EXCEED 16 BOXES
ER05 INPUT CORRECT FACTORY CODE
ER06 DELIVERY QTY SHOULD NOT EXCEED PRODUCT QTY
ER07 INCORRECT DATE
ER08 CANNOT ENTER A NAME
ER09 NOT EXSIST IN PILOT LOCATION CODE DATA
ER10 LOCATION CODE ALREADY DELETED
ER11 ASSIGN LARGER PILOT LOCATION CODE
ER12 NOT EXSIST IN PART DATA
ER13 FIRST PAGE
ER14 LAST PAGE
ER15 LOT NUMBER ALREADY DELETED
ER16 INPUT INSP DATA (Y OR N)
ER17 INPUT STOP DATE & STOP REASON
ER18 INCORRECT PROCESS CODE
ER19 INPUT HN LOCATION
